title: Xprim777
author: Xprim777
content: Hi, I would like to sell this LTC Bit Elevation set #6There are 6 notes in this set : 1,5,10,25,50,100 LTC.  I don't have many information about Bit Elevation.There are also BTC and XMR notes, but I think these are the only notes this merchant has made.Starting bid: 0.001 BTCMinimum bid increments : 0.0001 BTC End time : Thursday 1st June 2023, 23h UTC+2 (Paris time) - Countdown TimerSniping : Bids within 10 minutes before the auction end extend the auction for 10 minutes.Payment : 3GNqRESrurGcsBiqRvpGxRjsNf12FJtn2eShipping : $10 worldwide with trackingEscrow accepted, winner pays fees.
